    • applyThemeManager

      public void applyThemeManager​(String currentGuiLafTheme)
      Manages the set of Look and Feel Theme on the Application with a given Look and Feel String name, following 3 needed steps.

      The first step is to call the method themeSetter, which is the one in charge to apply the theme sending the Laf name to it as parameter.

      The second step is to call the FlatLaf method to update all the current Application UI.

      And the third step is to update properly the JFileChooser used to open and save Cinema Tickets files, calling the method in charge.

      Parameters:
      currentGuiLafTheme - The String Look and Feel name
